title: American horror story freak show - Final scene freaks eternal after life
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: its even sadder when you think about this being the very last moment we see Jessica in AHS  taking the stage to a large applaud. this was truly the best way to give our favorite mother of horror a goodbye.
I always cry when Penny says "we got married". She and Paul both had such hard lives, and they finally found peace and solace with one another.

It is so weird to know the last lines of Jessica Lange in AHS are "Am I to perform, now?" 

Btw, she is the best actress in the world. End of matter.

“Welcome Miss Elsa. I missed you.”

I CRIED SO HARD OMG
Everyone got the happy ending they deserved :,)
